c: 2
v: 223
t: "Sin Agbi sin Buqrek Toysa isin faxxa haytan kabuk sinni Buqrel fidoh xayyoowa xaylo edde geytaanamkeh, sinni Nafsih meqe taamoomiy Akeeral sin tanfiqe tatursuta, Yallak meesitaay Diggah isin Qhiyaamah Ayró kaat tangoorowoonu waytaanam ixiga, Nabiyow moominiin jannatal kaxxa maffaafal ken Aytukumus"